{"article_id":"fEmAQEMRZCwL8hJE","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Speaker of the House Nancy Pelosi , D-Calif. , arrives at the Capitol in Washington , Friday , Jan. 10 , 2020 .","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"Pelosi has n't relayed the articles of impeachment to the Senate for trial","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"three weeks","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"since President Donald Trump was impeached on charges of abuse and obstruction .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"Last night , she led the Democrat-controlled House","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"in passing a measure","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"limiting Trump 's ability","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"to take military action against Iran","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"after he ordered the U.S. killing of a top Iranian general .","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"( AP Photo/J . Scott Applewhite )","depth":4},{"id":10,"text":"Speaker of the House Nancy Pelosi , D-Calif. , arrives at the Capitol in Washington , Friday , Jan. 10 , 2020 .","depth":3},{"id":11,"text":"Pelosi has n't relayed the articles of impeachment to the Senate for trial three weeks","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"since President Donald Trump was impeached on charges of abuse and obstruction .","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"Last night , she led the Democrat-controlled House","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"in passing a measure","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"limiting Trump 's ability","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"to take military action against Iran","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"after he ordered the U.S. killing of a top Iranian general .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"( AP Photo/J . Scott Applewhite )","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"WASHINGTON","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"( AP ) -","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"Speaker Nancy Pelosi said","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"the House will take steps next week","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"to transmit the articles of impeachment against President Donald Trump ,","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"ending a three-week standoff","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"but confronting the Senate with only the third trial in U.S. history","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"to remove a chief executive .","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"In a letter to her Democratic colleagues , Pelosi said Friday","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"she was proud of their ''courage and patriotism \"","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"and warned","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"that senators now have a choice","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"as they consider the charges of abuse and obstruction against the president .","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"\" In an impeachment trial , every Senator takes an oath","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"to do ' impartial justice","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"according to the Constitution and laws , '''","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"Pelosi wrote .","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"\" Every Senator now faces a choice :","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"to be loyal to the President or the Constitution . \"","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"The trial could begin next week .","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"The Constitution gives the House the sole power","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"to impeach a president ,","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"but the Senate the ability","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"to render a verdict","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"when it convenes as the Court of Impeachment .","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"Pelosi was particularly upbeat Friday","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"as she strode through the Capitol ,","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"despite the mounting pressure on her","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"to quit delaying the trial .","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"Her decision","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"to end the showdown with Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"does not fully bring closure to the question","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"of whether the Senate will consider new witnesses ,","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"as some want ,","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"shifting pressure on senators","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"to decide .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"Trump swiftly signaled his intention","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"of blocking any testimony from John Bolton , the brash former national security adviser","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"who could be a wildcard witness in the trial .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"Bolton has said","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"he would appear before the Senate","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"if he received a subpoena .","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"At the same time , a key centrist GOP Sen. Susan Collins of Maine ,","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"whose vote is among those most watched ,","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"announced Friday","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"she was in discussions with other Republicans on a strategy","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"that would allow the Senate to hear new testimony .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"While the rules of Senate trial remain unsettled ,","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"the outcome is not .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"Trump is widely expected to be acquitted of the charges","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"that he abused power","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"by pressuring Ukraine to investigate Joe Biden ,","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"then obstructed Congress in its investigation .","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"No president has ever been removed by the Senate .","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"\" Ridiculous , \"","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"Trump told Fox News ' Laura Ingraham about the speaker ' s gambit .","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"\" Nancy Pelosi will go down as the least successful speaker of the House in the history of our nation , \"","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"Asked if he would invoke executive privilege","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"to block Bolton ' s testimony ,","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"Trump said ,","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"\" Well I think","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"you have to for the sake of the office . \"","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell ,","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"who has been working closely with the White House on strategy ,","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"said Friday afternoon","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"that the Senate is \" anxious to get started . \"","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"Republicans have the leverage , with a slim 53-47 Senate majority ,","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"if McConnell can keep GOP senators on board with his strategy .","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"So far , they are supportive of modeling the trial after the one","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"used in the last presidential impeachment , of Bill Clinton , 20 years ago .","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"It set out a path","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"for starting the trial","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"and voting on witnesses later .","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"Despite McConnell ' s wishes for a speedy trial ,","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"some Republicans in his caucus have indicated","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"that they are open to witnesses .","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"It takes just 51 senators to set the rules ,","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"and Democrats have been trying to win over wavering GOP senators","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"to vote with them on hearing new testimony .","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"\" I am hopeful","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"that we can reach an agreement on how to proceed with the trial","depth":13},{"id":101,"text":"that will allow the opportunity for witnesses for both the House managers and the President ' s counsel","depth":14},{"id":102,"text":"if they choose to do so , \"","depth":14},{"id":103,"text":"Collins said .","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"\" It is important that both sides be treated fairly . \"","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"Since the House vote on Dec. 18","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"to impeach the president ,","depth":6},{"id":107,"text":"the showdown between Pelosi and McConnell , the two power centers in Congress , has consumed Capitol Hill","depth":6},{"id":108,"text":"and scrambled the political dynamics .","depth":6},{"id":109,"text":"The speaker declined to send the articles to the Senate","depth":6},{"id":110,"text":"until she knew","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"there would be a fair trial with witness testimony .","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"She also asked McConnell for details on the trial structure","depth":7},{"id":113,"text":"she could decide who to appoint as impeachment managers .","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"McConnell rebuffed all over her demands .","depth":6},{"id":115,"text":"On Friday , Pelosi ended the stalemate","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"by saying","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"she had asked House Judiciary Committee Chairman Jerrold Nadler to be prepared to bring to the floor next week a resolution","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"to appoint managers","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"and transmit the articles of impeachment to the Senate .","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"She did not announce a date for the House vote .","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"McConnell indicated Friday","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"the trial would start soon .","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"\" We ' ll get about it as soon","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"as we can , \"","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"Transmittal of the documents and naming of House impeachment managers are the next steps","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"needed to start the Senate trial .","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"Yet questions remain in the Senate on the scope , format and duration .","depth":7},{"id":129,"text":"Senate Minority Leader Chuck Schumer is eager to test Senate Republicans , especially those like Collins","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"who are up for re-election in 2020 ,","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"with votes","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"to compel testimony from Bolton , acting White House chief of staff Mick Mulvaney and others","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"who have so far resisted appearing before Congress .","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"\" Senate Democrats are ready for the trial to begin","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"and will do everything","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"we can","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"to see","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"that the truth comes out , \"","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"Schumer said .","depth":9},{"id":140,"text":"Bolton ,","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"who was present for several of the internal White House discussions about Ukraine policy","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"that were at the heart of the Democrats ' impeachment case ,","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"is among the most compelling of four witnesses","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"suggested by Schumer .","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"The former national security adviser clashed with the president ' s Ukraine policy ,","depth":9},{"id":146,"text":"saying","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"he didn ' t want to be part of any \" drug deal \"","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"being cooked up .","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"He called Trump ' s personal lawyer Rudy Giuliani ,","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"who","depth":14},{"id":151,"text":"others have testified","depth":14},{"id":152,"text":"was orchestrating an alternative foreign policy outside of official channels ,","depth":13},{"id":153,"text":"a \" grenade \"","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"that was going to go off .","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"The House impeached Trump in December on the charge","depth":9},{"id":156,"text":"that he abused the power of his office","depth":10},{"id":157,"text":"by pressuring Ukraine ' s new leader to investigate Democrats ,","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"using as leverage $ 400 million in military assistance for the U.S. ally","depth":12},{"id":159,"text":"as it counters Russia at its border .","depth":12},{"id":160,"text":"Trump insist","depth":11},{"id":161,"text":"","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"e did nothing wrong ,","depth":10},{"id":163,"text":"ut his defiance of the House Democrats ' investigation led to an additional charge of obstruction of Congress .","depth":9},{"id":164,"text":"n a July telephone call with Ukraine ' s new president , Trump asked his counterpart to open an investigation into Democrat Joe Biden ,","depth":12},{"id":165,"text":"ho is running for his party ' s presidential nomination ,","depth":12},{"id":166,"text":"nd his son Hunter","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"hile holding up military aid for Ukraine .","depth":10},{"id":168,"text":"Ukrainian gas company had hired Hunter Biden","depth":10},{"id":169,"text":"hen his father was vice president and the Obama administration ' s point man on Ukraine .","depth":10},{"id":170,"text":"here is no evidence of wrongdoing by either Biden .","depth":8},{"id":171,"text":"t ' s still unclear who Pelosi will appoint as impeachment managers","depth":6},{"id":172,"text":"o prosecute the case in the Senate .","depth":6},{"id":173,"text":"adler , D-N.Y. , and House Intelligence Committee Chairman Adam Schiff , D-Calif. , will most likely lead the team .","depth":7},{"id":174,"text":"hat was more certain is that the group will be more diverse than the 1999 team in Clinton ' s trial ,","depth":8},{"id":175,"text":"ho were all male and white .","depth":8},{"id":176,"text":"elosi is expected to ensure","depth":7},{"id":177,"text":"he managers are diverse in gender and race , and also geographically .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":355,"left":196,"right":354,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":196,"left":187,"right":195,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":187,"left":0,"right":186,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":186,"left":185,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":185,"left":180,"right":184,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":180,"left":1,"right":179,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":179,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":184,"left":4,"right":183,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS